":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:45:08.000Z","msg":"後生十年既話第二球應該勉勉撲出"},{"pid":"0397e0a3bb5c753ef49e983104993eeb3e7be874","tid":269753,"uid":18143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>後生十年既話第二球應該勉強撲出</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ec0e6eaddc69c0e7a98acafa3636ee54de1245f","tid":269753,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T00:48:26.000Z","msg":"除左第三球 冇一球關"},{"pid":"22bdff37c962704b8724b76bd80e65fcd192ee01","tid":269753,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左第三球 冇一球關</blockquote><br />\n第三球反而唔得講佢喎<br />\n佢可以做既就淨係埋去封位<br />\n封左位 就睇對手射成點架啦"},{"pid":"72ebce2534903ad256d60cb65c52f362096efe13","tid":269753,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"覺得主要關後衛事<br />\n皇馬太多攻擊球員<br />\n後衛太少好易俾人拉散防線"},{"pid":"ff22829acca5fe17692be8726000c9a848458d69","tid":269753,"uid":85202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:51:24.000Z","msg":"第一球可以做得更好"},{"pid":"15a34289bbdecae0ee11dbc56862fb958295622a","tid":269753,"uid":85934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"其實我係認為冇責任，但俾人屌盲撐保方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02fb12871380e66ccf0359347878090687a7cfd8","tid":269753,"uid":5827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T02:10:41.000Z","msg":"第一球似做得唔夠好"},{"pid":"4a72c278c53c9b117e86754bef54b39a17eac07c","tid":269753,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"全部網仔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a6f79eeec018999017e35bbf4b51ed3527ecf8","tid":269753,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:13:54.000Z","msg":"第一球唔係省中邦路斯隻腳咩？"},{"pid":"31d37b86a08f77131c50b7402a354ea80838df64","tid":269753,"uid":17527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:24:54.000Z","msg":"第一球企位差少少<br />\n第二球死角仲要改變埋方向難搞<br />\n第三四球隊友唔mark人先失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844db5ed3b94d9eef93c66eb0e94441f64856279","tid":269753,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:27:11.000Z","msg":"第三球零距離又關佢事？<br />\n四球都唔係好關佢事<br />\n不過吹到銅牆鐵壁嘅祖記d 後衛竟然企喺度睇波"},{"pid":"aa9d84381a49cb75c6970467304dff7a922e00d6","tid":269753,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"第一球嚴格d係應該要移返中間快d<br />\n第二球冇得救 deflected<br />\n第三球要鬧既可能係有責任要提bonucci小心牙朗入攝<br />\n第四球冇得救"},{"pid":"486a6f1ef99c7abac523171a537d4d477260ba82","tid":269753,"uid":79622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"有無賽後highlight睇返"},{"pid":"ba0956bcd601ecd5801dcf17b5b6bd9612cbcd88","tid":269753,"uid":89709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"後衛責任多過保方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48438324ba7b73f720e811f474115b0f82b4d513","tid":269753,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"佢個人打法係偏向保守，所以四球都冇責任<br />\n<br />\n但俾著紐亞既，我諗第一球有機會救到，第二球出迎接左唔會俾人斬到咁深，第三球有機會行出左一步俾個波省中，第四球應該冇得玩<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得係第二同第三球有機會有啲肯出迎既龍門有機會避免到，例如vds、vv，第二球就算咁樣射到埋黎我覺得vds都可以屈手長救到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但保方已經做左佢本份，冇得怪佢"},{"pid":"7f3c380070eb87ecb8b64a81d7b4416b21e032be","tid":269753,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"無 都唔洗話要點點點同人比 你比紐亞守 佢一樣都會救唔到某樣波"},{"pid":"43de4c50792742b003ecb77e6c833a9c13111140","tid":269753,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無 都唔洗話要點點點同人比 你比紐亞守 佢一樣都會救唔到某樣波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得今場啲失波係咁岩對住佢個弱點黎搞，先搞到佢好似形同虛設咁<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪拖舟既部署，始終拖舟踢開波應該有啲心得<br />\n<br />\nbtw拖舟終於贏番意大利一次了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef37eb5c18bffacdf1de8e88f6dbd25c8c3ed76","tid":269753,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"第一，二球掂到人，改左少少方向<br />\n第三球根本冇人睇c朗 on99<br />\n第4太失望 訓左冇睇"},{"pid":"6abe76921b24bf5106189eb753584740ae591b63","tid":269753,"uid":15796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:09:15.000Z","msg":"第二球反應真係慢<br />\n睇返慢鏡就知<br />\n冇停左一下實救到"},{"pid":"d98c236b95cfa007782dd2e1b2ece3b8a1afefa8","tid":269753,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">南太雄點睇</span>"},{"pid":"f7239a86b4ad014e6f8c1fbfcf189faa8e827927","tid":269753,"uid":84815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二球反應真係慢<br />\n睇返慢鏡就知<br />\n冇停左一下實救到</blockquote><br />\n省中人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窒一窒好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要cur得咁靚<br />\n冇得怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e8170a2bc76490f8e7aa30e925402f39e2bc90","tid":269753,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"第二球佢判斷出界點知中伏"},{"pid":"e16f6c27eb7616939287aa81bd553000a4cb1d59","tid":269753,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二球反應真係慢<br />\n睇返慢鏡就知<br />\n冇停左一下實救到</blockquote><br />\n省中人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />窒一窒好正常啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要cur